<h2>The GIMP Pocket Reference</h2>
<p>
  <img class="icon" src="the_gimp_pocket_reference.png"
       alt=""
       width="100px"
       height="160px"/>
  <strong>Author:</strong> Sven Neumann<br/>
  <strong>Format:</strong> Paperback, 97pp.<br/>
