  <strong>Publisher/Date:</strong> O'Reilly &amp; Associates, Incorporated/August 2000<br/>
  <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/gimppr/">http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/gimppr/</a><br/>
  <br/>
  <strong>Description:</strong> The GIMP Pocket Reference explains the
